        {
            "title": "澳洲3月CPI大幅上揚但略低於預期;核心通膨持平",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yx5m80ObJELUhpLnMokzRA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPECA10T7_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 受中東戰爭導致的燃料和航運中斷影響,澳洲3月消費者物價指數通膨大幅上升,但數據略低於預期,核心通膨則保持穩定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲統計局(ABS)週三公布的數據顯示,截至3月31日的CPI年增4.6%。該數據略低於預期的4.8%,但較前一季度的3.7%大幅上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月CPI較前一個月增長1.1%,其中運輸成本因燃料價格上漲成為最大推動因素。這與美國-以色列對伊朗戰爭導致的全球油價大幅上漲趨勢一致。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-60b783f0-f088-3039-b7ea-5c55e2eb3820-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以修正均值CPI代表的核心通膨在3月上升3.3%,與前一個月持平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲統計局物價統計主管蘇-艾倫·盧克(Sue-Ellen Luke)在聲明中表示:\"3月的增幅是自2017年該系列數據開始以來最大的單月增幅,反映了中東衝突對燃料價格的影響。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">房價上漲也對3月通膨增長有所貢獻。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週三的數據反映了伊朗戰爭對燃料價格和通膨的影響。但數據也顯示潛在通膨有所穩定,特別是在澳洲儲備銀行今年兩次加息之後。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B23%E6%9C%88cpi%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8A%E6%8F%9A%E4%BD%86%E7%95%A5%E4%BD%8E%E6%96%BC%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E6%8C%81%E5%B9%B3-025331314.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 11:07:16",
