            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普準備對伊朗實施長期封鎖,《華爾街日報》報導",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7vsPtL1T0bhwOtrhhdrpEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_4_M_1440048337.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 據《華爾街日報》週二報導,美國總統唐納德·川普已指示助手為對伊朗實施長期封鎖做準備,這標誌著華盛頓在權衡衝突下一步行動時,轉向持續施加經濟壓力的策略。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報導援引美國官員的消息稱,川普選擇加強遏制伊朗石油出口的力度,並限制往返其港口的航運,認為封鎖比恢復大規模軍事打擊或尋求快速外交退出的風險更低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此舉是在4月停火之後採取的,當時停火結束了一場大規模轟炸行動,但該地區的緊張局勢仍然高漲。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2d5a5b82-cec6-3ec7-902a-9f6f62bb8cb5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》表示,川普最近拒絕了伊朗提出的三步驟提案,該提案原本會提前重新開放荷姆茲海峽,同時推遲核談判,川普認為該提案不足以滿足美國對德黑蘭核計劃施加限制的要求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導補充稱,川普不願放棄一項關鍵要求,即伊朗承諾暫停鈾濃縮活動至少20年,並在此期限之後接受限制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導稱,雖然封鎖被視為對伊朗經濟施壓的手段,但它也引發了長期對峙的前景,官員警告稱,隨著外交陷入僵局,衝突可能進入「無協議、無戰爭」階段。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
